Package uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.parquetstore.operation.addelements.impl.rdd

Additional classes used to maniplate RDDs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregateGafferElements
    Used to aggregate Elements.
    CalculateSplitPointsFromJavaRDD
    Generates the split points from an JavaRDD of Elements by selecting a sample of the data, sorting that sample and then pulling out the relevant objects to act as the split points
    ExtractKeyFromElements
    A function that will extract the key of an Element ready to aggregateByKey
    WriteUnsortedDataFunction
    This is a function used by Spark to write out a Spark RDD's partition of data to file.
